<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(١١٥٢)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الشَّيْخُ:</span> الصَّوَابُ <span class="c2">(مَمَاتُهَا)</span> وَلَكِنْ كَذَا <span class="c2">(مُصِيبَاتُهَا)</span> قاله الشيخ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>